What does this software do then?
================================

   XaoS is a realtime interactive fractal zoomer. This means that it
lets you zoom smoothly into any place in the fractal you choose without
the many hours of calculation required by most other fractal
generators. It now has many other features too, like 13 different
fractal types, autopilot, special coloring modes, support for various
bit depths (8bpp, truecolor, hicolor and realcolor), random palette
generation, color cycling etc...


