GGI driver
==========

   GGI stands for General Graphics Interface. Part of this project is
to develop libggi, a portable graphics library, and XaoS's GGI driver
uses that.  It is experimental, since the API of libggi is not
stabilized yet.  There are some problems with keyboard handling--the
shift key doesn't work yet.

   Everything else might work well, but there are no guarantees. It is
alpha quality software.

   GGI driver was written by Jan Hubicka, 1998.


