===================

   These functions are used to animate fractal state--to zoom, unzoom
and morph various parameters. They should be used only in animation
files.  Animations are usually performed for a time selected by an
immediately following timing function. *Note time::.  For example:

     (view 0 0 1 1)
     (morphview 0 0 2 2)
     (usleep 5000000)

   Will do a 5 second long unzooming animation.

